e end of the competition.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brilliant comeback\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium place\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His achievement was made all the more remarkable after only just scraping into Saturday's showpiece following a 12th-place finish in the semi-final, where he secured his spot by 0.25 points.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His achievement\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday's showpiece\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12th-place finish\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"0.25 points\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finishing in the last qualifying place meant Williams started first in each round of the final, something he believes worked in his favour.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last qualifying place\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"each round\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"his favour\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I am pretty shocked, I did bad earlier.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel like I did not deserve to get into the final.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the semi it was what I deserved, but I feel I am among those boys, like last year World Championships I came fourth, this year I came seventh.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those boys\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a crazy shock, but to medal is a different thing.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crazy shock\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"medal\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"a different thing\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually think it played in my advantage going first so I could only focus on myself.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my advantage\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even though I was following someone, there is a minute break between each round so it was just like training almost, go up there by myself, stand on the 10m for a while.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute break\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"each round\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10m\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It worked today so I can not complain.\\\"\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams looked set to miss out on a spot on the podium after some over-rotation on his fourth dive caused him to drop into fifth.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"some over-rotation\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"his fourth dive\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he delivered a brilliant response with scores of 93.60 and 94.35 on his final two dives which, combined with other results working in his favour, saw him claw a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brilliant response\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"scores\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"other results\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"his favour\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams admitted that he thought after the fourth dive that his competition was over.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth dive\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"his competition\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I'd messed up and I was like 'that's it, it's over,'\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't doing the fifth and sixth dive in my head like let us chase that medal again.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fifth and sixth dive\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"that medal\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd messed up and was like I have got my best two dives last, which is why they are there, I will just try and do them well.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best two dives\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For all I knew I was in tenth, so if I can bump myself up from tenth to top six.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like I will try and climb a bit but I wasn't thinking about medals at all.\\\"\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cao Yuan claimed gold, meaningChinatake a clean sweep of all diving gold medals at this Games, while Japan's Rikuto Tamai finished with silver.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cao Yuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Yuan\"}, {\"begin\": 2526, \"end\": 2531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9798182446398797, \"rank\": 0.014643729846098283, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean sweep\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"all diving gold medals\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams' team-mate Kyle Kothari had to settle for an 11th placed finish.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Busch\", \"score\": 0.999380498421194, \"rank\": 0.0005142458857536989, \"text\": \"Kyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Busch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Busch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an 11th placed finish\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Williams' second medal ofParis2024 after taking silver withTom Daleyin the men's synchronised event.\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams' second medal\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"ofParis2024\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"withTom Daleyin\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2723}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's synchronised event\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams dedicated his medal to his coach Dave Jenkins, who died in 2021, and opened up about his mental health struggles, but believes that diving is his \\\"form of therapy\\\".\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2797, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.9999986764807663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dave Jenkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"his medal\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"his mental health struggles\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"form\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"My mental health's always been pretty bad.\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My mental health\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have struggled with mental health for a long time, I have been on anti-depressants for a few years, so even without the grievance of Dave, my coach, I think it's just something I have to live with.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_ph